Sequence Information.Hemolytic Activity: No hemolysis information or data found in the reference(s) presented in this entry
Sequence Information.Function: Antifungal heat stable protein produced in response to injury. It is active against C.albicans. No antibacterial activity against Gram-positive and Gram-negative bacteria.
Sequence Information.Developmental stage: Highest expression in larvae and adult. To a much lesser extent in pupae.
